{"tid":797207,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳： 反擊濫炸律師信　守護公義基金幫手 鍾劍華籌款　大戰689 - 李八方","createTime":"2018-08-28T10:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T10:41:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab0eebaa327554cb867bf46618df38cd0373239","tid":797207,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180828/20486369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F20486369&d=y9%2F9aHg93Q5DxJqxdNSMdkzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=69bcead7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F20486369&h=bff98238\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180828/20486369</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月28日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n反擊濫炸律師信　守護公義基金幫手<br />\n鍾劍華籌款　大戰689 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180828/large/a1201a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180828%2Flarge%2Fa1201a.gif&h=c6bc672a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n前特首梁振英上周五再向理大應用社會科學系助理教授鍾劍華同《立場新聞》發律師信，告佢哋誹謗，鍾劍華噚日係facebook貼出689律師寄畀佢嘅法律文件，即係話689已正式開始司法程序入稟。鍾劍華日前已講明同689鬥到底，但打官司係燒錢玩意，鍾劍華肯定唔夠689錢多，幸好守護公義基金出手，將搞籌款支援佢嘅法律開支，實行集結民間力量對抗689。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180828/large/a1201b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180828%2Flarge%2Fa1201b.gif&h=483360c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾劍華噚日喺fb貼出689律師寄畀佢嘅法律文件。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180828/large/a1201c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180828%2Flarge%2Fa1201c.gif&h=84996057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\npo法律文件預備打持久戰<br />\n<br />\n鍾劍華噚日喺fb貼出一堆律師信，話終於收到文件，會先同律師朋友傾，但自己立場清楚堅定，有心理準備打場持久戰，又話已向守護公義基金會提出支援，仲會考慮眾籌。<br />\n<br />\n至於守護公義基金噚日宣佈信託人改組，同埋為鍾劍華籌款，發言人鄭宇碩對689告鍾劍華同《立場新聞》表示遺憾，認為威脅香港言論同新聞自由，由於鍾劍華正式向佢哋求助，而鍾又係基金信託人，為免利益衝突，鍾決定退出，工黨前立會議員何秀蘭就加入成為新信託人。<br />\n<br />\n基金成立至今已籌得超過1,200萬，扣除DQ案同佔中九人案嘅律師費，仲有約636萬，呼籲市民繼續支持佢哋，捍衞香港核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n李八方  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n蘋論︰ 以人性的惡掩蓋制度的惡 (李平)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 科學園搞AI速遞中心 (李八方)"},{"pid":"1765ad1a4353a30c55b9db560ec946bd8a9efb74","tid":797207,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"捐咗 $100 去守護公議基金<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bxzmFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bxzmFS</a>"}]}